{"tid":1126591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"他們曾說過……","createTime":"2019-04-26T13:22:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T13:22:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a6f0f12a264d3d94fe97111728015f5cc9a6f10a","tid":1126591,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T13:22:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190426/20664377\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190426%2F20664377&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3Tjs0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=8069e843\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190426%2F20664377&h=f6109931\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190426/20664377</a><br />\n<br />\n他們曾說過&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190426/large/a1102a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190426%2Flarge%2Fa1102a.gif&h=107243e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n學生與政府完全站到了對立的立場上。這時候偷笑的，應當就是李鵬和黨內的保守派了。他們通過「四二六」社論，既挑動了學生的情緒，又挾持鄧小平站到強硬立場，是成功的「一石二鳥」之計。<br />\n<br />\n可以說，六四事件本來就是一場由李鵬等人發動的，有組織，有預謀的，而最後以血腥代價取得成功的政變，而「四二六」社論就是這場政變的信號彈。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash; 八九學運領袖王丹在2009年的一期《開放》雜誌撰文，分析《人民日報》4.26社論的前因後果  <br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：六四30年：回流黃雀嘆港法治淪喪「九七後放咗班賊入嚟」<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n六四30年：回流黃雀嘆港法治淪喪「九七後放咗班賊入嚟」<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n蘋人誌：拍香港電影的中國導演 白雪<br />\n<br />\n六四30年：回流黃雀嘆港法治淪喪「九七後放咗班賊入嚟」"}]}